Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子…姐姐…？
