Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七尾英理子  三年前还住在我们附近的龙司的表姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来去美国留学了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候回来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家想尽早见到龙司嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是找我干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微去接点货  想要个男人来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先给你看这个  打开它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:35.11,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(348,240,278,240)}「SEVENTAILS」是保护世界的遗产=Lost Precious的团体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEVENTAILS？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我新建的团体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那输入名字试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜  您成功登录为「SEVENTAILS」的第一助手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像马车的马一般努力为英理子干活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  已经到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  还真亏你能得到「Society」的认可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看清楚点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:16.41,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-19\pos(300,235)}向现代世界遗物保护协会=Society申请中！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没认可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙都在无视我  说什么成员太少来当借口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是因为实绩太少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们有S级的遗物  他们也一定会改变态度的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是S级的可没那么容易见到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说今晚「Fang」在这交易货物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Fang」吗？！那  那个…难道你说的货是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得应该去报警比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话货就没我的份了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那或许是从我们家抢走的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  时间还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就先一边交流感情一边等晚上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  你长得越来越可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子姐  我听说「Fang」为获取遗物不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对上这种组织你有胜算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在美国弄到的哦  能制造引发奇迹了的假象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的主人是个魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在给黑手党的表演上扯什么「召唤蝴蝶大军」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被人家杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说这东西寄宿着他的怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  这可是真的遗物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:08:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的啦  又不是诅咒遗物  没有诅咒在上面的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在意着三年前的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没在意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的  那是S级的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是很危险的啦  英理子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上咯  龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻舞  蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  去拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么  快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子弹  是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气冲出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真周到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  方向盘交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻舞  萤火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子姐  前面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  拿好箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要遇上这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  行了  快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙…司…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  或许比S级还赚啊
Comment: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是久违了啊  龙司的家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫那么大声  等水电瓦斯能用了就给我立刻搬回去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  搞水电要打哪的电话啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩到底是怎么回事啊  你真的没头绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她知道龙司的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是…但是会放火的女孩要是我见过的话怎么可能忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会不会是这遗物的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了哦  所以给我看看你这项链…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  快拿开她拿开她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是食物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  龙司  龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我们在哪见过吗  为什么你会知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被粘上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jika lako nani？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯瓦西里语也不行  应该说她只懂说「龙司」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还说不认识  怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不认识啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  这么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:14:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交流非常困难  那线索就只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不会对你使坏的  乖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她偏偏就听龙司的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Society的列表上也找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是联系警察或者Society本部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话这个遗物不就不属于我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本来就是这孩子的东西吧  而且要是被发现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是团体申请不了  还会被教会除名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那龙司  今晚就让你来照顾她了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这孩子她只会粘着龙司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我哪懂照顾女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是要让我照顾？不是我吹嘘  后果很严重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好骄傲的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊  你丢得下这么依赖自己的女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么定了  既然话说完了  肚子也饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司快做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要给这孩子换洗的衣服啊  我给你卡你去买回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就两个女孩子为什么要这么多东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江藤同学  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  白天你把书包忘了  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你一直在这等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按门铃不就好了  英理子姐会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  龙司君  刚才那女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  快回来  快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江藤同学谢谢你  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子一看到龙司出去就开始闹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到她衣服都脏了所以领她去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我完全搞不定她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  然后我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她手腕上的绷带拆下来了  龙司快看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是看她的手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手背上的这个是龙的鳞片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子是传说中的幻兽  红龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司的料理真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂做饭的男人会很受欢迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客套话就不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没吃过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想吃吗  给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  你会成为一个好妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  她真的是龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都只是个人类的女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:18:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说龙的普通形态跟人类是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了在手背上的鳞片  龙纹以外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在成年之后才能变身成那种龙型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪查到这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些  我们竟然能弄到龙  太值了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片鳞片  就算是手指甲大小的都是S级的遗物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说  但这可不是我们能搞定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶紧找Society来接收才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来龙司  你在哪认识龙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没认识呢  而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  还是跟叔叔他们说一下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啦  这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正父亲和母亲肯定都在忙着搞其他的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来帮我忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得给她起个名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不光是让她叫龙司吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝怎么样？她手上的纹样像玫瑰一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的点子还真是意外的少女向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子  龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}龙司  萝丝  龙司  萝丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  英理子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}谜之生物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}有那种东西在这附近？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在学习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  我想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她能说话就好了  我有很多问题想问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  你想吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙比我想象中的还要庶民趣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子  冰淇淋冰淇淋冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对嘛  冰淇淋是女孩子的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子姐  冷静点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这  你不是跟英理子姐一起睡的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:20:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没察觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那早饭是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上  吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她昨天一直在看电视
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  我想吃味噌汤  这么久没回日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  请问这有龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪哒啪哒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.07,0:21:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪哒啪哒
